,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"아니, 그것뿐만은 아니에요.\n린코 선배는 누군가 고민하면 같이 생각해 주잖아요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event171-07-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"아, 네…… 잘 안 되서 곤란하거나……\n고민하는 마음은 저도 잘 이해하니까요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event171-07-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"하나의 문제에 시간을 너무 들이니까\n요령이 부족한 것 같긴 하지만요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf01_openeye","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event171-07-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"하지만, 그런 린코 선배이기에\n모두 도와주는 거라고요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event171-07-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"아리사","body":"자신을 위해 열심히 고민해주는 학생회장이니까\n무슨 일이 생겼을 때 힘이 되고 싶은 것 아닐까요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event171-07-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"그런 걸까요……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event171-07-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"믿음직한 학생회장…… 이라기엔 다를지 몰라도\n신뢰받는 학생회장이라고 느꼈어요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event171-07-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"린코 씨는 자신이 제가 생각하는 그런\n멋진 사람이 아니라고 하셨지만……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event171-07-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"그래도 역시 멋진 사람이라고 생각해요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event171-07-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"상대가 어떤 사람이든, 어떤 문제든…… 자신이 약한 것이라도\n린코 씨는 눈앞에 있는 것에서 절대로 눈을 돌리지 않아요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event171-07-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"도망치지 않고 계속 마주하는 강함을 갖고 있어요……\n그것이 제가 이 눈으로 본 린코 씨의 멋짐이에요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event171-07-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"고맙, 습니다……\n저도, 토모에 씨의 진짜 멋진 모습을 알 것 같아요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event171-07-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":